DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"Good data plans, but customer service is slow."}, 'Surveys'[Feedback])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'ServiceUsage'[DataUsage (GB)],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			"CountLastUsageDate", CALCULATE(COUNTA('ServiceUsage'[LastUsageDate]))
		)

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	VAR __DS0BodyBinnedSample = 
		SAMPLEAXISWITHLOCALMINMAX(
			3500,
			__DS0Core,
			'ServiceUsage'[DataUsage (GB)],
			[CountLastUsageDate],
			350,
			,
			ALPHABETICAL,
			ASC,
			105000,
			60
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
	"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount
)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyBinnedSample

ORDER BY
	'ServiceUsage'[DataUsage (GB)]

DEFINE
	VAR __H0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"Good data plans, but customer service is slow."}, 'Surveys'[Feedback])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Customers'[City],
			"TotalUsage", 'ServiceUsage'[TotalUsage],
			"ServiceUsageTotalUsage", IGNORE(CALCULATE('ServiceUsage'[TotalUsage], KEEPFILTERS(__H0FilterTable))),
			"AverageCallDuration__mins_", CALCULATE(AVERAGE('ServiceUsage'[CallDuration (mins)])),
			"ServiceUsageAverageCallDuration__mins_", IGNORE(
				CALCULATE(
					AVERAGE('ServiceUsage'[CallDuration (mins)]),
					KEEPFILTERS(__H0FilterTable)
				)
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(1001, __DS0Core, [TotalUsage], 0, 'Customers'[City], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	[TotalUsage] DESC, 'Customers'[City]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"Delhi"}, 'Customers'[City])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL('Surveys'[Feedback], "IsGrandTotalRowTotal"),
			ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL(
				'LocalDateTable_517cf939-268b-4f90-8882-47de9ec69442'[Year], "IsGrandTotalColumnTotal"
			),
			__DS0FilterTable,
			"AverageSatisfactionScore", CALCULATE(AVERAGE('Surveys'[SatisfactionScore])),
			"MinStatus", CALCULATE(MIN('SupportTickets'[Status]))
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(
			102,
			SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'Surveys'[Feedback], [IsGrandTotalRowTotal]),
			[IsGrandTotalRowTotal],
			0,
			'Surveys'[Feedback],
			1
		)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(
			__DS0Core,
			'LocalDateTable_517cf939-268b-4f90-8882-47de9ec69442'[Year],
			[IsGrandTotalColumnTotal]
		)

	VAR __DS0Secondary = 
		TOPN(
			102,
			__DS0SecondaryBase,
			[IsGrandTotalColumnTotal],
			1,
			'LocalDateTable_517cf939-268b-4f90-8882-47de9ec69442'[Year],
			1
		)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0PrimaryWindowed,
			SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
				__DS0Core,
				"ColumnIndex",
				__DS0Secondary,
				[IsGrandTotalColumnTotal],
				ASC,
				'LocalDateTable_517cf939-268b-4f90-8882-47de9ec69442'[Year],
				ASC
			)
		)

EVALUATE
	__DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
	[IsGrandTotalColumnTotal],
	'LocalDateTable_517cf939-268b-4f90-8882-47de9ec69442'[Year]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	[IsGrandTotalRowTotal] DESC, 'Surveys'[Feedback], [ColumnIndex]
